JOHANNESBURG - Members of the African National Congress, South African Communist Party, Hani family and other political officials are on Saturday commemorating the 28th anniversary of Chris Hani's killing. Hani was shot in the driveway of his home in Dawn Park, in the east rand of Johannesburg on 10 April 1993. WATCH LIVE: 28th Annual Chris Hani Commemoration  Download the Eyewitness News app to your iOS  or Android  device.